            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Attitudes, practices, and zoonoses awareness of community members involved in the bushmeat trade near Murchison Falls National Park, northern Uganda",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "BreeAnna M.",
